msgstr "Pó-liû uì kio̍k-pún su-tshut ê kiat-kó"

#: kconf_update/kconf_update.cpp:373
msgctxt "main|"
msgid ""
"For unit tests only: do not write the done entries, so that with every re-"
"run, the scripts are executed again"
