"Tan-uī tshik-tshì iōng: bái siá uân-sîng ê hāng-bo̍k, án-ne ta̍k-pái tîng-sin "
"tsip-hîng tshik-tshì ê sî-tsūn, kio̍k-pún mā ē tsò-hué tîng-sin tsip-hîng"

#: kconf_update/kconf_update.cpp:375
